1000:She'd cut it badly on glass during the earthquake. Sena had tried to stop the bleeding with a towel, but the cut turned out to be deeper than she'd thought. Kozue was going to need real medical attention.[%p]
1100:Gigalomaniac powers couldn't heal injuries.[%p]
1200:The pain made your brain realize the injury was real, whether you wanted it to or not.[%p]
1300:You couldn't create a shared awareness that the injury didn't exist. You couldn't make it so it never happened. Your human instincts wouldn't let you.[%p]
1400:[name]梢[line]I can't walk anymore, nora![%p]
