10800:Had he protected me? Me, of all people?[%p]
10900:Sena looked in disbelief at the blood spreading across the station's floor tiles.[%p]
11000:[name]波多野[line]Words are... chaos.[%p]
11100:Her father whispered with his dying breaths.[%p]
